    <div class="py-2">
      <text class="text-lg">
        I really love to learn and want to help people to learn better. I do research on game theoretical model of education and analyze evidence to make better decisions and design better interventions.<br>
        <b>Let's colaborate! </b>
      </text>
    </div>
    <div class="mt-8">
      <a class="btn" href="https://linkedin.com/in/barrysianturi" target="_blank"> Let's connect!</a>
      <a href="mailto:barrys.sianturi@gmail.com" target="_blank" class="btn btn-outline ml-5">
        Email me!
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div>
    <div class="text-3xl w-full font-bold mb-2">My last projects {"</>"}</div>
  </div>

  <HorizontalCard
    title="Ergodicity and Education"
